a) Dacă sunt indicate responsabilităţile în execuţia contractului şi interacţiunea între membrii echipei, inclusiv cele referitoare la managementul contractului, activităţile suport şi, dacă este cazul, distribuirea şi interacţiunea sarcinilor şi responsabilităţilor între operatorii din cadrul grupului (dacă este cazul), se acordă 12 puncte;
b) Dacă sunt indicate parţial responsabilităţile în execuţia contractului şi interacţiunea între membrii echipei, inclusiv cele referitoare la managementul contractului, activităţile de suport şi, dacă este cazul, distribuirea şi interacţiunea sarcinilor şi responsabilităţilor între operatorii din cadrul grupului (dacă este cazul), se acordă 8 puncte;
c) Dacă sunt indicate în mod limitat responsabilităţile în execuţia contractului sau interacţiunea între membrii echipei, inclusiv cele referitoare la managementul contractului, activităţile de suport sau distribuirea şi interacţiunea sarcinilor şi responsabilităţilor între operatorii din cadrul grupului (dacă este cazul), se acordă 4 puncte.
Nota 1: (...)DATORITA NUMARULUI LIMITAT DE CARACTERE SE VA CONSULTA OBLIGATORIU TEXTUL INTEGRAL PREZENTAT IN ANEXA 1 LA DOCUMENTATIA DE ATRIBUIRE

Punctajul tehnic se acordă astfel:
Ptehnic: (P2)+(P3)+(P4)+(P5)+(P6), unde:
- (P2) reprezintă punctajul acordat factorului de evaluare – componenta tehnică: experienţa deţinută de expertul-cheie MANAGER DE PROIECT;
- (P3) reprezintă punctajul acordat factorului de evaluare – componenta tehnică: experienţa deţinută de expertul-cheie ŞEF ECHIPĂ DE PROIECTARE – INGINER PROIECTANT CFDP;
- (P4) reprezintă punctajul acordat factorului de evaluare – componenta tehnică: experienţa deţinută de expertul-cheie ŞEF DE ŞANTIER – INGINER PROIECTANT CFDP;
- (P5) reprezintă punctajul acordat factorului de evaluare – componenta tehnică: Demonstrarea unei metodologii adecvate de implementare a contractului, precum şi o planificare adecvată a resurselor umane şi a activităţilor – Abordarea propusă pentru implementarea contractului;
- (P6) reprezintă punctajul acordat factorului de evaluare – componenta tehnică: Demonstrarea unei metodologii adecvate de implementare a contractului, precum şi o planificare adecvată a resurselor umane şi a activităţilor – Atribuţiile membrilor echipei în implementarea activităţilor contractului şi, dacă este cazul, contribuţia fiecărui membru al grupului de operatori economici, precum şi distribuirea şi interacţiunea sarcinilor şi responsabilităţilor dintre ei.
Punctajul total al fiecarei oferte se calculează pe baza formulei: Ptotal = Pfinanciar + Ptehnic

criteria_from_actual_contract_translated:
Technical component
The duties of the team members in implementing the contract activities and, where applicable, the contribution of each member of the group of economic operators, as well as the distribution and interaction of tasks and responsibilities between them – (P6): Demonstration of an adequate methodology for contract implementation, as well as adequate planning of human resources and activities – The duties of the team members in implementing the contract activities and, where applicable, the contribution of each member of the group of economic operators, as well as the distribution and interaction of tasks and responsibilities between them. The demonstration of an adequate methodology for contract implementation, as well as adequate planning of human resources and activities – The duties of the team members in implementing the contract activities and, where applicable, the contribution of each member of the group of economic operators, as well as the distribution and interaction of tasks and responsibilities between them will be scored as follows:
a) If the responsibilities in the execution of the contract and the interaction between team members are indicated, including those related to contract management, support activities and, where applicable, the distribution and interaction of tasks and responsibilities between the operators within the group (where applicable), 12 points are awarded;
b) If the responsibilities in the execution of the contract and the interaction between team members are partially indicated, including those related to contract management, support activities and, where applicable, the distribution and interaction of tasks and responsibilities between the operators within the group (where applicable), 8 points are awarded;
c) If the responsibilities in the execution of the contract or the interaction between team members are indicated in a limited manner, including those related to contract management, support activities or the distribution and interaction of tasks and responsibilities between the operators within the group (where applicable), 4 points are awarded.
Note 1: (...) DUE TO THE LIMITED NUMBER OF CHARACTERS, THE FULL TEXT PRESENTED IN ANNEX 1 TO THE AWARD DOCUMENTATION MUST BE CONSULTED.

The technical score is awarded as follows:
Ptechnical: (P2)+(P3)+(P4)+(P5)+(P6), where:
- (P2) represents the score awarded to the evaluation factor – technical component: the experience of the key expert PROJECT MANAGER;
- (P3) represents the score awarded to the evaluation factor – technical component: the experience of the key expert TEAM LEADER FOR DESIGN – CFDP DESIGN ENGINEER;
- (P4) represents the score awarded to the evaluation factor – technical component: the experience of the key expert SITE MANAGER – CFDP DESIGN ENGINEER;
- (P5) represents the score awarded to the evaluation factor – technical component: Demonstration of an adequate methodology for contract implementation, as well as adequate planning of human resources and activities – The proposed approach for contract implementation;
- (P6) represents the score awarded to the evaluation factor – technical component: Demonstration of an adequate methodology for contract implementation, as well as adequate planning of human resources and activities – The duties of the team members in implementing the contract activities and, where applicable, the contribution of each member of the group of economic operators, as well as the distribution and interaction of tasks and responsibilities between them.
The total score of each offer is calculated based on the formula: Ptotal = Pfinancial + Ptechnical

